main event: A civilian observed a round white object in the sky for approximately 5 minutes on May 7, 1964, in Cresco, Iowa.
interesting points: The object was observed moving south at a high altitude., The sighting lasted for about 5 minutes., No physical evidence of the object was found., The weather included a thunderstorm in the area during the sighting., The witness was a gas company employee whose identity was withheld.
